    Black Aracnia stood at the head of the hatch. She held her bowcaster and 
then let the ramp dpwn until she saw the form of Darmouse. Aracnia knew if 
she had Quickstrike she could control the vermine.
    "Well, are you coming in or not? And, remember, I hold your commanders 
life in my claw. One wrong move and he's as good as dead." She hissed at 
Darkmouse.
